      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$6,400 - Honest poor-condition driver/project being sold as-is. It runs and moves, but it shows significant wear throughout, with noticeable cosmetic flaws, a tired interior, and the kind of deferred maintenance and age-related issues a buyer should expect from a budget fixer-upper. This is not a clean turn-key example; it\u2019s better suited for someone looking for an inexpensive project, parts car, or basic transportation they are willing to sort out. Expect visible imperfections inside and out, and plan on repairs and reconditioning if you want to bring it up to a higher standard.",
