      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, a practical runaround, or a handy parts donor? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward budget buy with plenty of potential for the right person. It\u2019s being offered as a no-frills, honest car for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC and wants something they can tinker with without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re realistic, handy, and after value, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
