    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest used car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the powertrain pulls well, the transmission shifts through the gears, and it remains a solid candidate for a daily beater, backup car, or project. Suspension and chassis feel serviceable, and it\u2019s the kind of vehicle you buy for dependable point-A-to-B duty without paying for showroom cosmetics. If you want an affordable car with usable mechanicals and room to improve over time, this one is worth a look.",
